# <type>(<scope>): <short summary>  ← 72 chars max, imperative mood
#
# Types:  feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | perf | test | chore | ci
# Scope:  optional, e.g. auth | sessions | bot | milestones | admin | frontend
#
# Body (optional) — wrap at 72 chars, explain WHY not WHAT:
#
#
# Footer (optional):
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   Closes #<issue>
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CHANGELOG reminder:
#   Before committing a user-facing change, add a line to CHANGELOG.md
#   under the [Unreleased] section using one of:
#     ### Added | Changed | Deprecated | Removed | Fixed | Security
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
